data.description: STUNNING 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 3-car garage home situated on a sprawling 2-acre lot. This Gary Robinson built home is TV worthy! Step into the lap of comfort and style with over 2500 square feet of thoughtfully designed open-concept living space. This ranch-style gem features a gourmet kitchen, massive pantry, spacious living area with a fireplace, and a master suite with a spa-like bathroom. A bonus room above the 3-car garage offers flexibility for your needs. The expansive lot provides endless outdoor possibilities.
